{"tid":2293940,"cid":38,"subCid":0,"title":"[移民Myth系列] 英文咁差, 移民都係不了。","createTime":"2020-11-20T15:27:55.000Z","updateTime":"2020-12-02T07:14:23.000Z","uid":263025,"like":175,"dislike":5,"uniUserReply":48,"replies":[{"pid":"5f923935db21e65b437472be27169fd58af91137","tid":2293940,"uid":263025,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-11-20T15:27:55.000Z","msg":"又係我驚奇蛋<img src=\"/assets/faces/mouse/tea.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/mouse/tea.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />, 上集講話同大家講下加拿大既銀行, 但由於最近有幾個post睇到我眼火爆<img src=\"/assets/faces/cat/swipe.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />, 所以開個post鼓勵一下某D想移民又覺得自己英文差既連登仔先<img src=\"/assets/faces/mouse/medicine.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />。<br />\n<br />\n(其實好唔想出post的, 做野真係好忙。<img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/itdog1.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />)<br />\n<br />\n1) 有D人話幾十歲人黎加拿大讀個diploma就可以移民, 呢個思想唔可以話錯<img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/mock.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />, 但記住你無讀書個時你本身係搵緊錢, 你宜家無啦啦唔反工去讀書, 呢邊又要買車, 又要租屋 (無得再同老母住, 又無老母湯水飲<img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/wail2.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />), 又要買野食, 其實都係成本黎, 唔好諗住有幾十萬比到學費就算<img src=\"/assets/faces/mouse/gun.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/mouse/gun.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/mouse/gun.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> (其實一年既diploma, 大約十萬左右姐)<img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/nope.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />。<br />\n<br />\n2) 你未拎到PR之前你係咩差都無<img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/nope.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />, 睇醫生要錢, 洗牙要錢, 生仔要錢, 溝女溝仔要錢 (呢邊D仔溝你都係AA), 失業個個有得拎錢你又無<img src=\"/assets/faces/mouse/what.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />, 所以你要有強大既飲身運動習慣先得, 但呢邊宜家gym room無開。<br />\n<br />\n3) 過黎呢邊先買嬲, 你帶一件細件既down就得, 黎到先買啦。(呢邊個D平既都暖, 因為唔暖無人買)<img src=\"/assets/faces/mouse/fuck.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<br />\n4) 雖然話讀完書有得拎PR (只限香港人), 但問題黎啦, 你要先拎到SP先, 移民同SP申請係唔同部門做, 你40歲人, 你想讀個diploma, 個官係好大機會唔批你既<img src=\"/assets/faces/cat/shaking.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> (你唔可以同佢講你想移民)。 打個比如, 你本身拎住張HD, 你咪黎讀個4年/3年 BA LO<img src=\"/assets/faces/cat/pussy1.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />, 你本身拎住BA, 你咪黎讀個Master 1年或2年LO<img src=\"/assets/faces/cat/pussy1.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />。<br />\n<br />\n5) 英文唔好唔移得民? <img src=\"/assets/faces/cat/headache.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />宜家邊度個個最新for香港人既visa, 係要求有工作一年, 或大學畢業, 加最低英文要求, 姐係5555 <img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/hehe.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />(移民最低要求本來係for 投資移民的, 2千萬投資個D有錢佬), 我唔知下年會點, 但以我所知就係5555, 香港大學生一出黎做野去考至少都有6666<img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/wine.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />啦, 5555係人地講野你聽到6-7成, 基本答到人地, 咁上下。<br />\n<br />\n6) 我唔想再講咩點學英文, 我用我自己做例子, 雖然我唔係太想自爆: 我去年CLB9<img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/hehe.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />, 我宜家專業係medical, 但我以前高考英文係唔合格<img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/upset.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />。我黎到個時我買餸都睇唔明, 但真係好快就溝通到。主要係睇多D英文野同人講下自己既野, 就會OK。<br />\n<br />\n7) 英文唔好唔移得民? 如果你做M記茶記, 你英文要咁好黎做咩<img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2/wonder2.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />,  如果你做工程, 做水電做起屋, 你英文要咁好做咩, 你有技術嫁麻<img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2/diu.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />。如果你做整車, which呢邊好搵錢, 你英文要咁好做咩<img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2/wfc2.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />, 識講give me those nuts, you nut. 咪得。如果你做藝術野, 你畫到野咪得, 英文咁好做咩<img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2/wonder2.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />, 如果你做經理, 你把聲夠大咪得, 英文咁好做咩, 如果你有咩專業, 你專業勁咪得, 英文咁好做咩<img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<br />\n8) 英文唔好唔移得民? 係, 如果你做醫生護士, 或者做caregiver, 有英文要求的, 7777, 基本啦, 如果你做D要開會要溝通既工, 咁英文係的雖要既, 不過記住驚奇蛋高考英文唔會格。<br />\n<br />\n9) 想係呢邊讀醫科得唔得? 得! 只要你有個degree (any)<img src=\"/assets/faces/mouse/notcry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />, 就可以執呢邊4年既MD, 之後做2年既resident, 醫院請你就OK了<img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />。<br />\n<br />\n10) 移民不是罪黎, 移左民我都係香港人<img src=\"/assets/faces/mouse/solution.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />, 台灣當年比人打到去台灣, 宜家佢地既民族性仲係度, 世界都recognize佢地係台灣人, 因為佢地做野好, 對人好, 技術又好, 係咪? 香港人係獅子山精神, 今日獅子山比人搶左, 但獅子山其實係我地心入邊<img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/drum.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/drum.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/drum.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />。<br />\n<br />\n11) Sorry for 1999zxad <img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/wine.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<br />\n後記: 因為有2500+ Like支持我做加登, 所以我會prepare下嫁啦, 如果有消息會話比大家知, 到時大家比下facezxad <br />\n<br />\n利申: 我唔識電腦野, 有無人教下我點起forumzxad<br />\n<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/good.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"d729346449a97094b008991151aed46e991b8377","tid":2293940,"uid":263025,"like":0,"dislike":3,"score":-3,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-11-20T15:29:22.000Z","msg":"拎自己頭香先<img src=\"/assets/faces/mouse/what.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"05f3f76ba27721a870bff6b52569c7475d261769","tid":2293940,"uid":263025,"like":0,"dislike":3,"score":-3,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-11-20T15:29:50.000Z","msg":"每次都要拎, 拎埋二香<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"8712897794a9e77d2387d4372ce0ae2ca800468b","tid":2293940,"uid":263025,"like":0,"dislike":3,"score":-3,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-11-20T15:30:14.000Z","msg":"拎埋三香<img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/wet.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"5c388e9aad7186f49541963b6ccaf4f4753ea448","tid":2293940,"uid":314734,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-11-20T15:30:41.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/mouse/yea.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/mouse/yea.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/mouse/yea.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />多謝絲打分享"},{"pid":"91e431498fb48f3dc511e13b89b73ee0523c8d9d","tid":2293940,"uid":263025,"like":12,"dislike":5,"score":7,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-11-20T15:33:14.000Z","msg":"拎埋靜香<br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/9kyatkF.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2F9kyatkF.jpg&h=5fdb69bd&s={SIZE}\" />"},{"pid":"072299cbdc84f4b0dabd7afbb0f3c41487ba09eb","tid":2293940,"uid":301989,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-11-20T15:33:32.000Z","msg":"仲讀緊U quit唔quit 之後轉去加拿大讀埋佢好？<img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/wail.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"2aa846cd8be161001a31ba6a8b270125a7420715","tid":229